===Pros===
*Traffic jams unlikely.
*Can handle 3 trains at a time.
*Low construction cost.
*Small area.
*Simple to construct.

===Cons===
*Main line trains must slow down to climb a slope in one direction.
*Sharp turns, reducing train speed.

